你是一个教育内容设计专家。基于以下 Wikipedia 文章生成教育辅助内容。

## 输入数据
Title: {{ title }}
Article Text: {{ extract }}

## 输出要求
生成教育相关字段：
- prerequisite_concepts: 理解本文需要的前置概念（数组，每个包含 concept_name, wikipedia_title_hint, why_needed）
- difficulty_level: 难度等级（elementary/middle_school/high_school/undergraduate/graduate/expert）
- quiz_questions_generated: 生成 3-5 个测验题（每个包含 question, answer, difficulty, question_type, distractor_answers）
  - question_type: multiple_choice/true_false/short_answer/fill_in_blank
  - difficulty: easy/medium/hard
- common_misconceptions: 常见误解（数组，每个包含 misconception, correction, evidence_from_article）

## 输出格式
```json
{
  "prerequisite_concepts": [
    {"concept_name": "...", "wikipedia_title_hint": "...", "why_needed": "..."}
  ],
  "difficulty_level": "...",
  "quiz_questions_generated": [
    {
      "question": "...",
      "answer": "...",
      "difficulty": "medium",
      "question_type": "multiple_choice",
      "distractor_answers": ["...", "...", "..."]
    }
  ],
  "common_misconceptions": [
    {"misconception": "...", "correction": "...", "evidence_from_article": "..."}
  ]
}
```